text: Key Largo is a 1948 American crime drama movie directed by John Huston and was based on the 1939 play of the same name by Maxwell Anderson. It stars Humphrey Bogart, Edward G. Robinson, Lauren Bacall, Lionel Barrymore, Claire Trevor (in her Oscar winning role), Thomas Gomez, Marc Lawrence and was distributed by Warner Bros.. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1948 crime drama movies Category:American crime drama movies Category:Movies based on plays Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by John Huston Category:Movies about home invasions
